data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION! Stunning spacious home, 2 story, 4 bedroom 3.5 bath w/attached sun room (many uses for this spacious area). Hardwood floors in most area downstairs, plantation shutters, high ceilings, corner oversized lot, 3 car tandem garage & Generac Generator 22KW. Kitchen features a breakfast bar, island, stainless steel appliances, walk-in pantry w/open concept. Primary bedroom is located on the 1st floor, updated on suite w/large walk-in shower w/built in bench, jetted tub & sizable primary closet. Relax in heated/cooled sunroom (approx. 700 sq ft) overlooking the back yard. Back yard oasis featuring an inviting jetted cocktail pool/hot tub w/waterfall, and outdoor kitchen. Sprinkler system front & back w/7 zones. Security system, 24 hr recordings & main box is under warranty. Woodlands ISD, easy access to I-45, shopping & hospitals. A/C units fairly new. Property has a rain barrel for rainwater catch. This property has never flooded. Tandum garage has a/c & heat.
